@startuml
participant Caller
participant cbsComment.cls
participant dbComment.cdComment
participant TrsRaiseError
Caller -> cbsComment.cls: GetComment(v_aryEmpNum, v_dtStartDate, v_dtEndDate)
activate cbsComment.cls
alt No Error
  cbsComment.cls -> dbComment.cdComment: CreateObject("dbComment.cdComment")
  activate dbComment.cdComment
  dbComment.cdComment --> cbsComment.cls: l_objComment instance
  deactivate dbComment.cdComment
  cbsComment.cls -> dbComment.cdComment: GetComment(v_aryEmpNum, v_dtStartDate, v_dtEndDate)
  activate dbComment.cdComment
  dbComment.cdComment --> cbsComment.cls: l_adrsComment (ADODB.Recordset)
  deactivate dbComment.cdComment
  cbsComment.cls --> Caller: l_adrsComment (ADODB.Recordset)
else Error Occurred (GetComment_Err)
  cbsComment.cls -> TrsRaiseError: TrsRaiseError(m_strCMODULENAME, "GetComment", ...)
  activate TrsRaiseError
  TrsRaiseError --> cbsComment.cls: Error Handled
  deactivate TrsRaiseError
  cbsComment.cls --> Caller: Nothing
end
deactivate cbsComment.cls
@enduml